include ../svg-icon/svgIcon

.question-dropdown-wrapper
  a.question-dropdown__item
    .question-dropdown__item__icon
      +svgIcon("share")
    span Teilen
  a.question-dropdown__item
    .question-dropdown__item__icon
      +svgIcon("paintbrush")
    span Bearbeiten
  label.question-dropdown__item.question-dropdown__item--with-toggle(data-target="qNotificationsToggler")
    span.question-dropdown__item__toggle-wrapper
      span
        span.question-dropdown__item__icon
          +svgIcon("bell-crossed")
          +svgIcon("bell")
        span Mitteilungen
      span.question-dropdown__item__toggle.item-toggle
        input(type='checkbox')
        span.item-toggle__slider
    span.question-dropdown__item__hint
      | (Sie erhalten Mitteilungen &uuml;ber neue Antworten und Kommentare)
